Get to know the Shocker experience

At Wichita State, there's more to see, do and experience than you'll ever find in                            the typical college town. From time-honored traditions and hundreds of annual on-campus                            events to a city teeming with arts and culture, Shockers can have it all.

Simply put, life's good in Wichita. This means Shockers not only benefit from unmatched                            access to area employers, they also enjoy the high-quality, low-cost, amenity-rich                            living found in the world's Air Capital.
An education for the real world
At Wichita State, every degree we offer takes your education far beyond the classroom—equipping                            you with practial experience you can apply to your career from day one.
It's one thing to read about the unmatched opportunities, resources and experiences                   found on Wichita State's 330-acre campus. It's another to see it for yourself.
Having someone who’s done it before teach me how to do it – that’s the most valuable                   experience that I’ve gotten.

Badge Courses at Wichita State University
WSU Workforce Education and Badge Programs

The Office for Workforce, Professional and Community Education (WPCE) is your link to University workforce training and professional development programs.  The WPCE can provide information regarding the many career-relevant academic programs and certifications the University offers.

Need a workforce prepared to compete in a global society?  The WPCE works with employers to develop customized training tailored to meet your organization's needs in regards to content, schedule and training location.
The WPCE also offers numerous conferences and workshops that enhance job skills and meet state and national requirements for professional relicensure.
Browse our training calendar and catalog to find a program that fits your professional and personal learning needs.  If you do not see a class you are looking for, please
